      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they don't get it. talking to people just feels like... like putting a bandaid on a gaping wound. it doesn't change the fact that he's gone. the silence in this house is heavy. it's like the world just stopped and i'm the only one still being forced to move through it. it's exhausting.",
